"cid": 248489, "create_time": 1655974711, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re 洞主: 查了一下，5月份CPI和PPI涨的品类分别是：从同比看，CPI上涨2.1%，涨幅与上月相同。其中，食品价格上涨2.3%，涨幅比上月扩大0.4个百分点，影响CPI上涨约0.42个百分点。食品中，鲜果、薯类和粮食价格分别上涨19.0%、16.1%和3.2%，涨幅比上月均有扩大；鲜菜和鸡蛋价格分别上涨11.6%和11.4%，涨幅比上月分别回落12.4和1.9个百分点；猪肉价格下降21.1%，降幅比上月收窄12.2个百分点。非食品价格上涨2.1%，涨幅比上月回落0.1个百分点，影响CPI上涨约1.68个百分点。非食品中，汽油、柴油和液化石油气价格分别上涨27.6%、30.1%和26.9%；宾馆住宿和飞机票价格分别下降7.4%和2.4%。\n\n 从同比看，PPI上涨6.4%，涨幅比上月回落1.6个百分点。其中，生产资料价格上涨8.1%，涨幅回落2.2个百分点；生活资料价格上涨1.2%，涨幅扩大0.2个百分点。调查的40个工业行业大类中，价格上涨的有37个，与上月相同。主要行业中，价格涨幅回落的有：煤炭开采和洗选业上涨37.2%，回落16.2个百分点；有色金属冶炼和压延加工业上涨10.4%，回落6.4个百分点；石油煤炭及其他燃料加工业上涨34.0%，回落4.7个百分点；化学原料和化学制品制造业上涨13.6%，回落1.3个百分点。价格涨幅扩大的有：燃气生产和供应业上涨22.0%，扩大1.3个百分点；农副食品加工业上涨3.7%，扩大1.1个百分点；电力热力生产和供应业上涨9.7%，扩大0.4个百分点。黑色金属冶炼和压延加工业价格下降1.3%，是2020年9月份以来同比首次下降。\n\nhttp://www.stats.gov.cn/xxgk/jd/sjjd2020/202206/t20220610_1858006.html\n\n看来猪肉价格下降影响最大，其次宾馆飞机等因为疫情影响价格也下降了，能源价格涨幅和其他国家相似。", "timestamp": 1655974711}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248525, "create_time": 1655975634, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re 洞主: Re 洞主: https://www.zhihu.com/question/527228893 看了一圈，既然物流成本在上升，但CPI还是不涨，难道不是需求下降供过于求的原因吗，这有什么好吹的呢", "timestamp": 1655975634}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248567, "create_time": 1655976811, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 因为共存对经济造成了巨大冲击，欧美能维持现在的经济增长水平，得靠降息印钱大水漫灌，于是不可避免地造成了通货膨胀。", "timestamp": 1655976811}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248584, "create_time": 1655977231, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 那为什么清零不会通货膨胀，要知道美联储放水影响的是全世界，包括我国", "timestamp": 1655977231}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248612, "create_time": 1655978123, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: https://toyokeizai.net/articles/-/541379 日本把这个现象总结为デフレスパイラル（通缩螺旋），也就是消费减少导致物价下跌，物价下跌导致企业控制成本，企业控制成本导致消费减少。减少的消费被存到银行。所以就算PPI增长，日本的物价也很难增长。感觉日本已经在中国前方招手了。。。", "timestamp": 1655978123}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248613, "create_time": 1655978126, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Eve: 核心原因肯定是掌握足够的生产能力啊", "timestamp": 1655978126}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248617, "create_time": 1655978251, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re 洞主: 因为所谓マークアップ率（价格/成本）很低，所以日本企业很多都没办法控制价格，无法把成本转嫁到价格", "timestamp": 1655978251}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248621, "create_time": 1655978355, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 我国的能源价格和世界接轨，也涨20%多，说明物流成本肯定大幅上涨；另外PPI涨幅也很高，因为仍然有很多原材料要从外国进口。什么叫有足够的生产能力？", "timestamp": 1655978355}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248646, "create_time": 1655978911, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 美联储印钱肯定会影响我国，也就是所谓的输入型通胀。但是影响的程度肯定要比美国低。通胀的直接的原因是钱多货少，越接近生产中心通胀的影响就越小。", "timestamp": 1655978911}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248650, "create_time": 1655978992, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 但是所有的工业品价格都上涨了，为什么消费端的商品价格不上涨呢，我们虽然接近生产中心，但生产中心的原材料还是由外国运进来啊", "timestamp": 1655978992}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248651, "create_time": 1655979063, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: dz是经管的同学吗", "timestamp": 1655979063}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248660, "create_time": 1655979136, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 否", "timestamp": 1655979136}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248667, "create_time": 1655979299, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 你看看cpi的算法，很大一部分是食品决定的。粮食生产自给自足没受到太大影响。", "timestamp": 1655979299}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248672, "create_time": 1655979361, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 工业品的原材料只占出厂价格的一部分，大部分附加值是国内完成的，所以影响有限。", "timestamp": 1655979361}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248675, "create_time": 1655979389, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 粮食里面蔬菜价格也大涨（感觉是物流价格的问题），倒是猪肉价格不知道为什么大跌", "timestamp": 1655979389}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248680, "create_time": 1655979445, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 猪周期而已。", "timestamp": 1655979445}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248692, "create_time": 1655979658, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 那ppi是怎么算的，它包括附加值之类的吗", "timestamp": 1655979658}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248704, "create_time": 1655980094, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 如果忽略猪周期的影响，我国cpi会不会大幅高于现在的数值", "timestamp": 1655980094}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248714, "create_time": 1655980331, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: ppi侧重原材料的价格。ppi长期高于cpi，中央经济会议给出的定性是“供给冲击，需求收缩，预期减弱”。供给端通胀终究没能压过需求端的通缩。", "timestamp": 1655980331}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248734, "create_time": 1655980682, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 好的，感谢eve", "timestamp": 1655980682}], "create_time": 1655973081, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1655980682, "likenum": 6, "n_attentions": 6, "n_comments": 36, "pid": 71217, "poll": null, "reply": 36, "text": "很疑惑清零和cpi不涨啥关系，以及为什么共存就和通胀有关系？有清零派给我解释一下吗", "timestamp": 1655973081}}